messageBody:
chasstw wrote:

> How I can test a method with diferent set of data ?. Does it possible
> to test it in one execution time ?
> It's must be very simple, but I'm a newbie.

It's not simple. You want a Parameterized Test Case. I suggest searching
the archives of this list for the phrase "Parameterized Test Case". A
few descriptions will be in there.
